    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boxel 3D is a speedrunning game packed with challenging levels, custom skins, online multiplayer, and a creative level editor. No internet? No problem. Play offline to beat your high scores.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208440/extras/b9096c4488337fd2054a12406f598a17.avif?t=1755006062\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 50 levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online multiplayer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Custom skins</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level editor</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mods</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208440/extras/dbe808ce2832d266bcfc0bd2ce1b180a.poster.avif?t=1755006062\" width=600 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208440/extras/dbe808ce2832d266bcfc0bd2ce1b180a.webm?t=1755006062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208440/extras/dbe808ce2832d266bcfc0bd2ce1b180a.mp4?t=1755006062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208440/extras/ec5fba24112dc2f15a8b9ace95e3e0d6.avif?t=1755006062\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Boxel 3D Workshop is now live and ready for the most creative level designers to participate. Not much of a designer? Be sure to support your designers by voting or commenting on their creations.</p>",
